    <intervention_model_description>Randomized double blind placebo-controlled for at least 15 months, followed by an open label extension phase of up to 12 months.
The placebo-controlled phase, will end when the last patient randomized will perform his 15 months evaluation (visit 7). Then all patients will be treated with the active drug during an open-label extension phase for a total study duration of 27 months.</intervention_model_description>
